Create Slave
SyncState *

# mailbox.org

MaildirStore andreser@mailbox.org-local
Path ~/mail/andreser@mailbox.org/
Inbox ~/mail/andreser@mailbox.org/INBOX

IMAPStore andreser@mailbox.org-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
User andreser@mailbox.org
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
SSLType IMAPS
PassCmd "cat $HOME/.keyring/andreser@mailbox.org.txt"

Channel andreser@mailbox.org
Master :andreser@mailbox.org-remote:
Slave :andreser@mailbox.org-local:
Patterns *
Sync PullNew PullFlags PushFlags

# MIT Exchange over IMAP with strict TLS and CA pinning
MaildirStore andreser@mit.edu-local
Path ~/mail/andreser@mit.edu/
Inbox ~/mail/andreser@mit.edu/INBOX

IMAPStore andreser@mit.edu-remote
Host imap.exchange.mit.edu
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
SSLType IMAPS
SystemCertificates no
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/GeoTrust_Global_CA.pem
User andreser
PassCmd "cat $HOME/.keyring/andreser@mit.edu.txt"
PipelineDepth 200

Channel andreser@mit.edu
Master :andreser@mit.edu-remote:
Slave :andreser@mit.edu-local:
Patterns INBOX "Sent Items"
Sync PullNew PullFlags PushFlags

# krutt.org, with strict TLS

MaildirStore andres@krutt.org-local
Path ~/mail/andres@krutt.org/
Inbox ~/mail/andres@krutt.org/INBOX

IMAPStore andres@krutt.org-remote
Host mail.autistici.org
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
SSLType IMAPS
SystemCertificates no
# sudo sh -c 'curl http://www.autistici.org/static/certs/ca.crt > /etc/ca-certificates/trust-source/anchors/autistici-ca.crt'
CertificateFile /etc/ca-certificates/trust-source/anchors/autistici-ca.crt
User andres@krutt.org
PassCmd "cat ~/.keyring/andres@krutt.org.txt"

Channel andres@krutt.org
Master :andres@krutt.org-remote:
Slave :andres@krutt.org-local:
Patterns *
Sync PullNew PullFlags PushFlags

